---
title: Cheesy Chorizo and Sweetcorn Pizza with Tomatoes and Cheddar
description: This Cheesy Chorizo and Sweetcorn Pizza is a crowd pleaser and is one to get the family round the dinner table for. Super simple to make, and easily customised to suit the kids too.
